gles-major-lazer-registers-a-no-1-hit-with-bieber-and-mo-20160731|title=Australian Singles: Major Lazer Registers a No 1 Hit with Bieber and M\u00d8|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=31 July 2016|accessdate=1 August 2016}}</ref>\n| ''[[This Unruly Mess I've Made]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Boasty]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">([[Wiley (rapper)|Wiley]], [[Stefflon Don]] and [[Sean Paul]] featuring Idris Elba)</span>\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2019\n| 11 || \u2014\n|\n* [[British Phonographic Industry|BPI]]: Platinum<ref name=\"bpi\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bpi.co.uk/brit-certified/|title=BRIT Certified - bpi|publisher=[[British Phonographic Industry]]|accessdate=26 April 2019|format=To access, enter the search parameter \"Boasty\" and select \"Search by Keyword\"}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\" {{TBA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Come Alive\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(Wrenne featuring Idris Elba)</span><ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/gb/album/come-alive-feat-idris-elba-single/1453550265|title=Come Alive (feat. Idris Elba) - Single by Wrenne|website=iTunes|accessdate=20 November 2019}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"New Breed\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(James BKS featuring [[Q-Tip (musician)|Q-Tip]], Idris Elba & [[Little Simz]])</span><ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/gb/album/new-breed-feat-q-tip-idris-elba-little-simz-single/1486177988|title=New Breed (feat. Q-Tip, Idris Elba & Little Simz) - Single by James BKS|website=iTunes|accessdate=20 November 2019}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n| colspan=\"6\" style=\"font-size:90%\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart or was not released in that territory.\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{sisterlinks|d=Q342604|c=Category:Idris Elba|n=no|b=no|s=no|wikt=no|species=no|m=no|mw=no|v=no|voy=no}}\n* {{official website}}\n* {{IMDb name|252961}}\n* {{Tcmdb name}}\n* {{Amg name|270025}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title = [[Li