itics' Choice Television Award for Best Movie/Miniseries Actor}}\n{{GoldenGlobeBestActorTVMiniseriesFilm}}\n{{Independent Spirit Award for Best Supporting Male}}\n{{NAACP Image Award for Outstanding Supporting Actor in a Motion Picture}}\n{{ScreenActorsGuildAward MaleSupportMotionPicture}}\n{{ScreenActorsGuildAward MaleTVMiniseriesMovie}}\n}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Elba, Idris}}\n[[Category:1972 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:English people of Ghanaian descent]]\n[[Category:English people of Sierra Leonean descent]]\n[[Category:20th-century English male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century English male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century English musicians]]\n[[Category:Black English male actors]]\n[[Category:Black British male rappers]]\n[[Category:Best Miniseries or Television Movie Actor Golden Globe winners]]\n[[Category:British house musicians]]\n[[Category:Electronic dance music DJs]]\n[[Category:Club DJs]]\n[[Category:English DJs]]\n[[Category:English expatriates in the United States]]\n[[Category:English male film actors]]\n[[Category:English film producers]]\n[[Category:English music video directors]]\n[[Category:English male rappers]]\n[[Category:English record producers]]\n[[Category:English male voice actors]]\n[[Category:English male stage actors]]\n[[Category:English male television actors]]\n[[Category:English television producers]]\n[[Category:English male kickboxers]]\n[[Category:Independent Spirit Award winners]]\n[[Category:Male actors from London]]\n[[Category:National Youth Theatre members]]\n[[Category:NME Awards winners]]\n[[Category:Officers of the Order of the British Empire]]\n[[Category:People from Hackney Central]]\n[[Category:People from Canning Town]]\n[[Category:People from East Ham]]\n[[Category:Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Miniseries or Television Movie Screen Actors Guild Award winners]]\n[[Category:Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Supporting Role Screen Actors Guild Award w